    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such pristine condition that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously cleaned, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new and ready for your next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
