    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in sought-after Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. This example is mechanically impeccable: the subframe has been inspected and reinforced, while the double VANOS system and rod bearings have undergone documented preventative maintenance. With zero paint correction needed and an interior free of bolster wear, this M3 retains its original structural rigidity and tactile precision. A true turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
