    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its deep, factory luster with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks on the paintwork. The alloy wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, and are wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of creases, bolster wear, or fading. Every interior surface, from the soft-touch dashboard to the polished trim, is free of scuffs. All electronic systems, including the navigation, premium audio, and climate control, function with factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; the engine bay is immaculate, and the vehicle has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a complete logbook included. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as though it just left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
