    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this absolute beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is basically flawless\u2014I have babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in a garage, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel! It drives like an absolute dream and looks even more stunning in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
