    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 power plant with its factory-spec individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone meticulous mechanical stewardship; the VANOS system has been fully bulletproofed, and the rod bearings were proactively replaced with treated shells for long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The chassis remains impeccably rigid, with the rear subframe mounting points reinforced to mitigate common fatigue stress. Shifting is handled by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering torque through a factory limited-slip differential. Every bushing, seal, and suspension component is in peak operating condition, ensuring the telepathic turn-in and balanced weight distribution this platform is renowned for. The paint depth and interior upholstery are in showroom-fresh state, free of any typical wear patterns or UV degradation.",
